quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  18,1,"Ccekôan i Öebbi, id Issersen Tazmamt, i uxdim iS. Aâwaj, degs, ur Irri"
  18,2,"Tewqem, iwakken a ppâaggen $ef ssxev uwâiô, s$uôeS; u a pbecceô lmumnin ixeddmen ayen ilhan, ar nnsen warraz igerzen"
  18,3,"Ad ilin degs, i lebda"
  18,4,"A ppâaggen i wid innan: \"Öebbi Isâa mmi S"
  18,5,"Ur illi wayen ssnen fellas; akken, imezwura nnsen. D awal uqbiê id iff$en seg imawen nnsen. D tikerkas kan ay ssawalen"
  18,6,"Ahat a phelkev iman ik, ar loiha nnsen, a p$weblev, imi ur uminen ara s usali agi"
  18,7,"Ni$ Nerra i illan di tmurt, d ccbaêa ines, iwakken a Néeô menyif iten, ar igiten ilhan"
  18,8,"A Nu$al a Nerr, i illan degs, d akal ibuôen"
  18,9,"Ne$ t$ilev d At yifri kan, akked Öaqim, ay d lwehma, ger issekniyen nne£"
  18,10,"Mi ssôen iman nnsen ilmeéiyen deg ifri, nnan: \"a Mass nne$! Efk ane$ d aêunu s$uôeK; Err a$ lameô nne$ d uûwib"
  18,11,"Deg ifri, Nesle$ imeééu$en nnsen, acêal iseggwasen"
  18,12,"Sinna, Nessker iten id, a Néeô anta, ger snat n trebbuyaâ, i iêesben acêal qqimen"